parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.Explain what? There is nothing that can be done now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.It was a one-time thing… It won't happen again.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl@>.It’s not true! That was Ella’s account!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.It doesn’t matter. You can't be the face of the operation anymore.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.What a vulture… Foxx can’t help herself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.You’re on my undercover team now. We can use this to disconnect you from the station.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlDe.It means you’ll be operating under a new set of rules.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.You’re a rogue agent now. You’ll follow my lead.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Meet me at my home later this afternoon. I’ve got a mission for you and Nellie…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.You two are going to finish this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp.Clean out your desk. You’re off the force…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.You’re going to be escorted off the premises.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp.As far as anyone is concerned, you’re finished here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp.You’ll make it up to me, 1Hero. Believe me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.God damn it… Serves me right for trusting that Tasha girl.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaDe.Why the hell did she record us?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp.As far as anyone is concerned, you’re finished here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp.You’ll make it up to me, 1Hero. Believe me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Erica… Lillian’s maid and the priest from Eve Cathedral… They went to check up on her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Duncan has new goons and the mansion is crawling with them…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.They got captured and we had to break out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.You know Duncan is there. Tell me what’s going on.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.What did you expect? We had to find Lillian.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.That woman has disappeared. She’s probably not even at the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.We did and she was chased away… We don’t know where she is now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Father Solomon and Erica are now in danger. Duncan knows about them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.They aren’t in danger. I’ll handle this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Forgive me for not simply trusting you, but these people are innocent bystanders. I need to know exactly what’s going on.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.I’ll go to the cathedral and personally meet with the priest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Because I have Duncan under tight control.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlDe.Trust me. He won’t be bothering them anymore.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Move along, 1Hero. I have other work to attend to.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Father Solomon is expecting something from us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.I told you: I’ll meet with him personally.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Father Solomon is expecting something from us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.I told you: I’ll meet with him personally.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.It’s some sort of card scanner. I wonder what it does.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I wonder what would happen if I used my electromagnet on this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeWoEx^.The cops showed up! I shot at them, but…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.They got arrested. What else could we have done?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.What the hell was Bhatt doing at the warehouse?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.She tells me an anonymous tip came in about Jon’s warehouse…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.Paul must have been listening on the scanner too… Damn.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeWoEx^.The place was packed. It didn’t go down like you said.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Even if it had, Duncan was missing. Sounds like the whole plan failed on that front…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.But what does it matter now? We need to find Duncan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Kimberly is going to want an interview and we’re not telling her about Duncan…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.It doesn’t matter what they say. The Guild dies tonight.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFrOp^.Does this mean I’m a free woman?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.This isn’t over for you, Miss Cole.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Is the Guild operation finished? What about the bigger team? There are more of us, right?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.Don’t worry about anyone but yourself, 1Hero. I’ll deal with closing the case.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeHaEx^.Let me go on the news. I can spin a story that’ll keep everyone off your tail.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.It just so happens that Kimberly is interested in a live interview.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe.Then our future here is on your shoulders.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnOp^.If the Guild case is closed, what the hell am I supposed to do now?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnDe^.Well… While you have plans, I've lost my place to stay.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.You’ll come home with me. We can discuss our future there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeSaOp^.You promised my record would be cleared.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.And you promised to kill Duncan’s henchmen.");
